---
title: Fresh Mozzarella and Spicy Marinara Pizza with Greens and Pepper Salad
description: It's pizza night and there's nothing better than a perfectly crisp base for our bell pepper, leek and cheese topping! We're kicking things up with a spicy marinara sauce and fresh mozza. It's oh so ooey, gooey and tasty!
